# xwai

**Unified AI integration.** Single API for OpenAI, Anthropic, local LLMs; natural language commands, context management; integration with xwentity, xwstorage, xwaction, xwbots. Per project docs.

*Full features and integration examples: [README_LONG.md](README_LONG.md).*

**Company:** eXonware.com · **Author:** eXonware Backend Team · **Email:** connect@exonware.com  
**Version:** See [version.py](src/exonware/xwai/version.py) or PyPI. · **Updated:** See version.py (`__date__`).

[![Status](https://img.shields.io/badge/status-alpha-orange.svg)](https://exonware.com)
[![Python](https://img.shields.io/badge/python-3.8%2B-blue.svg)](https://www.python.org)
